import React from 'react'
import {
    SidebarContainer,
    Icon,
    CloseIcon,
    SidebarWrapper,
    SidebarLink,
    SideBtnWrap,
    SidebarRoute,
    SidebarMenu
} from './SidebarElements'


const Sidebar = () => {
  return (
    <SidebarContainer>
        <Icon>
            <CloseIcon />
        </Icon>
        <SidebarWrapper>
            <SidebarMenu>
                <SidebarLink to="about">About</SidebarLink>
                <SidebarLink to="services">Services</SidebarLink>
                <SidebarLink to="signup">Sign Up</SidebarLink>
            </SidebarMenu>
            <SideBtnWrap>
                <SidebarRoute to="/signin">Sign In</SidebarRoute>
            </SideBtnWrap>
        </SidebarWrapper>
    </SidebarContainer>
  )
}

export default Sidebar
